    <title>CTL Helper</title>
    <link href="https://jose-rodrigues.info/blog/ctlhelper/" />
    <updated>2018-03-31T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <id>https://jose-rodrigues.info/blog/ctlhelper/</id>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;While developing with sqlldr, I made a tool to speed up some boring work (like making those freaking huge control files...)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;downloads&quot;&gt;Downloads&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/4thokage/ctlfx/releases/tag/1.0.0-RELEASE&quot;&gt;v1.0 - Release files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maven:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-xml&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;dependency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;groupId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;pt.zenit.oracle&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;groupId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;artifactId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;ctlfx&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;artifactId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;1.0.0-RELEASE&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;dependency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;what-does-it-do&quot;&gt;What does it do?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well it&#39;s a simple JavaFX app that generates some files for you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connects to specified oracle DB and reads all user tables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generates a Loader/Extractor CTL based on the chosen tables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</content>
